      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom condition, having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage under a fitted cover. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original deep factory luster without a single stone chip, swirl mark, or blemish. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the alloy wheels are pristine with no curb rash. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free from any bolster wear or creasing, and still carries a hint of that new-car aroma. All technological features, from the high-fidelity sound system to the precision climate control, operate exactly as they did the day it left the dealership. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians. The engine bay is detailed and dry, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, having never seen inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire an example that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
